==English==
===Etymology===
From French [[je ne sais quoi#French|je ne sais quoi]], literally ‘I don't know what’.

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/ʒə nə seɪ kwɑ:/}}

===Idiom===
'''[[je]] [[ne]] [[sais]] [[quoi]]'''
# an intangible quality that adds makes something attractive or alluring
#:''She has a certain '''je ne sais quoi about her.'''''


